    <name>FlameGet</name>
    <summary>A GTK4 Download Manager wrapping Aria2, Curl, and YT-DLP</summary>
    <description>
        <p>A blazing fast, lightweight downloader built for speed and reliability. From native browser integration and full torrent support to auto-merging high-quality media, FlameGet handles it all seamlessly.</p>
    </description>
